body_html: I have also seen this behavior. Profiling shows that (at least one major) bottleneck is Encapsulator::GetFunctionNameAttr inside EncapsulateXlaComputationsPass, which itself is mostly AttrSlice::Find—this call seems to take >10s cumulatively.
